### MongoDB Demo API - Health Check and Basic Endpoints
### Base URL: http://localhost:3001

### Health Check
GET http://localhost:3001/health
Accept: application/json

###

### Get All Available Queries
GET http://localhost:3001/api/queries
Accept: application/json

###

### Get Specific Query Details - Basic Find
GET http://localhost:3001/api/queries/basic-find
Accept: application/json

###

### Get Specific Query Details - Advanced Filtering
GET http://localhost:3001/api/queries/advanced-filtering
Accept: application/json

###

### Get Specific Query Details - Aggregation
GET http://localhost:3001/api/queries/aggregation
Accept: application/json

###

### Get Specific Query Details - Text Search
GET http://localhost:3001/api/queries/text-search
Accept: application/json

###

### Get Specific Query Details - Geospatial
GET http://localhost:3001/api/queries/geospatial
Accept: application/json

###

### Get Database Statistics
GET http://localhost:3001/api/data/stats
Accept: application/json

